ution problems. I\'m checking if the simulation is updating and if the particles are moving towards target positions, as that wasn\'t previously clear. I\'m focusing on texture formats, particularly whether `FloatType` is supported in the Cloud Run environment\'s Chrome instance. I\'m also considering the possibility of fallback render target issues or incorrect updates to `uCurrentPosition`. The initial donut appearance is concerning, so I need to verify that the shader runs correctly.\n\n\n"
